    <briefdescription>
<para>System that drives automatic game state transitions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1gamestate_1_1systems_1_1GameFlowSystem" kindref="compound">GameFlowSystem</ref> monitors the current <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1gamestate_1_1types_1a8e0bcae228fdf9f4cb489e7f912d80be" kindref="member">GameState</ref> and issues StateCommands to advance the state machine when appropriate. It tracks the previous state and transition ID to avoid emitting duplicate commands.</para>
<para>Typical flow: Undefined -&gt; Start -&gt; Title.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1gamestate_1_1types_1a8e0bcae228fdf9f4cb489e7f912d80be" kindref="member">GameState</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
